Tolonglah. Aku mohon.

64
00:03:26,442 --> 00:03:29,695
Tolong temukan kakakku.

65
00:03:30,029 --> 00:03:33,282
- Tolong temukan dia.
- Kumohon padamu.

66
00:03:43,834 --> 00:03:44,877
Itu dia?

67
00:03:47,379 --> 00:03:48,881
Bukan kakakmu.

68
00:03:54,136 --> 00:03:55,387
Kau tak apa?

69
00:03:56,597 --> 00:03:58,057
Tiap kali kau bilang bukan dia,

70
00:04:00,351 --> 00:04:01,811
