96
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:41,261
Su-hyeon!

97
00:06:43,806 --> 00:06:46,975
Putriku, Su-hyeon! Ya, Tuhan.

98
00:06:47,810 --> 00:06:48,811
Su-hyeon! Tolonglah...

99
00:06:52,606 --> 00:06:53,732
Su-hyeon!

100
00:06:59,154 --> 00:07:01,740
Memang terlihat dia tewas karena jatuh,

101
00:07:01,991 --> 00:07:03,909
