123
00:08:09,433 --> 00:08:11,018
Aku minta maaf.

124
00:08:11,727 --> 00:08:13,395
- Namun, Dae-yong, ini...
- Hei!

125
00:08:15,397 --> 00:08:18,025
Aku bukan hanya mau menyelamatkan diri.

126
00:08:19,109 --> 00:08:21,945
Sudah kubilang, ada alasan kuat!

127
00:08:22,237 --> 00:08:23,072
Maksudmu?

128
00:08:25,074 --> 00:08:26,116
Para atasam

129
00:08:27,117 --> 00:08:29,119
