130
00:08:30,454 --> 00:08:33,207
Kau tak bisa berkeliaran
dan menggali kuburan seenaknya.

131
00:08:34,458 --> 00:08:36,710
- Aku akan terlihat bagaimana?
- Ini pembunuhan.

132
00:08:37,461 --> 00:08:38,796
Choe Su-hyeon dibunuh.

133
00:08:39,463 --> 00:08:40,839
Kasus ini harus dikubur?

134
00:08:41,423 --> 00:08:43,258
Ada kaitan dengan kasus Jeong Sang-hun.

135
00:08:43,342 --> 00:08:46,595
Kau sendiri bilang, setidaknya
jasad Jeong Sang-hun harus ditemukan!

136
00:08:47,596 --> 00:08:49,056
Meski tidak,

137
00:08:49,139 --> 00:08:52,559
korban kasus yang kita tangani
ternyata dibunuh.

138
00:08:52,851 --> 00:08:53,977
Dia tidak bunuh diri.

139
00:08:54,394 --> 00:08:56,105
Kau mau tutup mata?

140
00:08:57,022 --> 00:08:58,023
Begitu?

141
00:08:59,149 --> 00:09:01,860
Aku tak bisa. Harga diriku melarangnya.

142
00:09:06,448 --> 00:09:10,577
Aku tahu posisimu sulit.
Aku memahami situasimu, tapi...

143
00:09:11,245 --> 00:09:12,496
Jika kita mengabaikannya,

144
00:09:14,248 --> 00:09:15,541
itu tidak benar.

145
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,794
Tae-sik.

146
00:09:20,838 --> 00:09:22,381
Pulanglah ke kampung halamanmu.

147
00:09:25,092 --> 00:09:26,301
Agar aku bisa hidup

148
00:09:27,427 --> 00:09:29,179
tanpa harus mengkhianatimu,

149
00:09:30,222 --> 00:09:31,723
itulah jalan terbaik.

150
00:09:33,642 --> 00:09:35,269
Pulanglah diam-diam.

151
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,650
Kubatalkan.

152
00:09:48,282 --> 00:09:50,159
Kutarik permintaan pemindahanku.

153
00:09:52,202 --> 00:09:53,162
Aku tak bisa pergi.

154
00:10:05,465 --> 00:10:07,384
KUNCI

155
00:10:07,467 --> 00:10:11,972
KOMISARIS JENDERAL PARK DO-SIK

156
00:10:16,143 --> 00:10:17,269
Kau sudah tiba.

157
00:10:19,688 --> 00:10:22,274
Halo. Maaf, aku belum memperkenalkan diri.

158
00:10:22,608 --> 00:10:24,151
Selamat atas penunjukkanmu.

159
00:10:24,651 --> 00:10:25,986
- Duduklah.
- Baik.

160
00:10:34,077 --> 00:10:36,580
Jadi, kau Kapten Yu Dae-yong?

161
00:10:36,663 --> 00:10:37,915
Ya.

162
00:10:37,998 --> 00:10:40,125
Aku sudah tahu
