163
00:10:40,709 --> 00:10:41,919
Kau pasti sedang sibuk.

164
00:10:42,002 --> 00:10:43,837
Tidak apa.

165
00:10:43,921 --> 00:10:46,715
Kau pasti sibuk menyelidiki Bareun News.

166
00:10:48,467 --> 00:10:50,677
Aku jadi sakit kepala, tahu?

167
00:10:50,761 --> 00:10:53,555
Aku yakin kau sudah dengar.

168
00:10:54,181 --> 00:10:56,975
Komisaris Jenderal sebelumnya
mengundurkan diri karena itu.

169
00:10:58,352 --> 00:10:59,227
Maafkan aku.

170
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:04,107
Kau tahu? Api menyembur
dari bawah ke atas.

171
00:11:04,775 --> 00:11:07,027
Saat polisi junior terlalu antusias,

172
00:11:08,403 --> 00:11:11,907
polisi senior akan terancam tanpa alasan.

173
00:11:12,908 --> 00:11:16,119
Kau mau mengalaminya sendiri?

