Jika ditutupi...

176
00:11:21,541 --> 00:11:24,294
Kurasa kau salah paham.

177
00:11:25,629 --> 00:11:26,713
Kau pikir

178
00:11:28,006 --> 00:11:30,467
peringatan ini berasal dariku?

179
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,723
INFORMASI

180
00:11:44,564 --> 00:11:45,816
Permisi.

181
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:48,902
Di mana aku bisa bertanya tentang artikel?

182
00:11:48,986 --> 00:11:50,612
Mohon tunggu. Biar kuperiksa.

183
00:11:50,696 --> 00:11:52,114
Bu Kim Seo-hui?

184
00:11:53,323 --> 00:11:54,658
Kita belum pernah bertemu.

185
00:11:55,242 --> 00:11:57,703
- Maaf, kau siapa?
- Silakan ikut ke kantorku.

186
00:12:04,918 --> 00:12:06,878
Kau pasti sibuk. Ada apa kemari?

187
00:12:07,629 --> 00:12:08,505
BAREUN NEWS, NAM SU-MI

188
00:12:08,588 --> 00:12:09,840
Silakan duduk.

189
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:15,595
Kita bisa buat janji
untuk bertemu lain kali.

190
00:12:15,679 --> 00:12:17,014
Itu hal yang lumrah.

191
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:22,561
Jadi, kenapa datang jauh-jauh ke kantorku?

192
00:12:23,228 --> 00:12:24,771
Ini soal Wartawan Choe Su-hyeon.

193
00:12:26,898 --> 00:12:28,442
Detailnya tak bisa kujelaskan.

194
00:12:30,736 --> 00:12:33,989
Namun, entah bagaimana,
kurasa kasusnya dan suamiku berkaitan.

195
00:12:35,073 --> 00:12:37,826
Kucoba mencari artikel Bu Choe,

196
00:12:38,493 --> 00:12:41,329
tapi tak ada di Internet.
Semuanya dihapus.

197
00:12:43,248 --> 00:12:44,666
Tolong katakan alasannya.

198
00:12:48,045 --> 00:12:51,006
Choe Su-hyeon,
sudah mati pun masih merepotkan.

199
00:12:52,883 --> 00:12:54,509
Kudengar, jenazahnya diautopsi.

200
00:12:56,136 --> 00:12:57,387
Mohon maaf.

201
00:12:57,721 --> 00:12:58,847
Lalu Yeong-min?

202
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:02,142
Sudah kau kendalikan?

203
00:13:03,310 --> 00:13:04,352
Ya.

204
00:13:05,437 --> 00:13:06,730
Aku tak tahu

205
00:13:07,731 --> 00:13:09,357
