00:18:28,259 --> 00:18:30,762
Turuti perintahku. Kenapa terus membantah?

317
00:18:32,806 --> 00:18:35,684
Jika mau membangkang, keluar dari timku.

318
00:18:36,726 --> 00:18:38,103
Maafkan aku.

319
00:18:47,195 --> 00:18:48,113
Hei, ambil separuh.

320
00:18:56,413 --> 00:18:57,664
Dae-yong.

321
00:18:58,331 --> 00:18:59,666
Bisa bicara?

322
00:19:12,178 --> 00:19:13,221
Jin-gyeong.

323
00:19:14,055 --> 00:19:14,973
Kau tak apa?

324
00:19:16,307 --> 00:19:17,559
Apa aku keterlaluan?

325
00:19:18,601 --> 00:19:20,729
- Tidak juga.
- Kenapa dia membentakku?

326
00:19:21,688 --> 00:19:25,900
Kurasa penyelidikan kita
harus dirahasiakan saat ini.

327
00:19:27,819 --> 00:19:29,070
Karena masalah itu, 'kan?

328
00:19:38,079 --> 00:19:40,165
- Kau tak berubah pikiran?
- Kau masih selidiki

329
00:19:40,248 --> 00:19:41,750
