00:20:06,191 --> 00:20:07,525
Kenapa berbuat sejauh ini?

339
00:20:10,695 --> 00:20:13,656
Katamu, para atasan
tak suka kita menyelidikinya.

340
00:20:13,823 --> 00:20:14,908
Maksudmu,

341
00:20:15,658 --> 00:20:18,453
