00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:33,676
Itu saja?

348
00:20:37,305 --> 00:20:38,223
Tae-sik.

349
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:40,475
Jika kau

350
00:20:41,142 --> 00:20:43,812
mau menyelidiki semaumu,
silakan ke luar timku.

351
00:20:46,189 --> 00:20:47,315
