00:27:57,027 --> 00:27:58,404
Tidak, aku tak tahu.

448
00:27:59,238 --> 00:28:01,866
Entah apa topiknya,
tapi sepertinya cukup penting.

449
00:28:01,949 --> 00:28:03,200
Su-hyeon jadi sensitif.

